    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Roof Mounted Strobe Light (Optional)</title>
        <para>The roof warning light is located on the center section of the roof structure or as may required by the
            state or local governing authority. The light is available (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f4700651">Fig. 51</hotlnk>) in different types and styles. These lights are generally in use
            during times when students are in transit on the bus.
        </para>
